REM
REM  How to run several MOPAC2009 jobs with one command.
REM
REM  Use the program "MOPAC2009 for all windows" version of MOPAC.
REM  Do NOT use the program "MOPAC2009 for WINDOWS XP" - if you do
REM  it will request a finish dialogue ("Program finished with exit code 0.
REM  Exit Window?) 
REM
REM  Use commands of the following type to run all the jobs.
REM
 call mopac2009.exe job1
 call mopac2009.exe job2
 call mopac2009.exe job3
 call mopac2009.exe job4
